## Name of the node
-name ${ERL_NODE_NAME}

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie partisan

## Explicit connections only (Deprecated in latest versions)
-connect_all false
-auto_connect never
-hidden

## Disable disterl
-start_epmd false
-erl_epmd_port 27781

## Increase distribution port buffer size.
## +zdbbl 32768

## Enable multi_time_warp
+C multi_time_warp
